>Description:
This is a feature request: the Check Syntax Error Message
window that is inserted whenever there is a Check Syntax
error should be resizable.  As is, you only get about
3 lines of visible text and have to scroll through the
message, which can be substantially longer, especially in 
Typed Scheme.
